title: Converse Takeaway Show from Pitchfork Paris: Jessie Ware "Running"
description:
Fresh from the stage, Jessie Ware took a quick break from Pitchfork festival to perform this acoustic Takeaway Show for La Blogotheque, Pitchfork TV, and Converse.

Track: "Running"
